{
  "texts": [
    "We computed the Vina scores from the generated pdbqt files using the score function from the Python interface of Vina (all scripts can be found via the GitHub page of Vina).",
    "The experimental B factors were parsed from published PDB files of crystal structures.",
    "For data cleaning, we omitted structures for which 80% of the published B factor values had the same entry.",
    "Additionally, for some structures, it was not possible to parse the B factors correctly due to inconsistencies in the underlying PDB files.",
    "The RMSF of each atom of the MD simulation was calculated after superposition to the first frame using pytraj 31."
  ]
}